fields.name: Available
fields.description: True if the name is available, otherwise false.

fields.name: Message
fields.description: A message explaining why the name is unavailable. Will be undefined if the name is available.

fields.name: Name
fields.description: The name whose availability was checked.

fields.name: Reason
fields.description: The reason code explaining why the name is unavailable. Will be undefined if the name is available.
